        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Gotu kola, kava kava, St. John's wort, valerian may increase CNS depression. FOOD: None known. LAB VALUES: May decrease total free thyroxine (T4) serum levels. May increase serum cholesterol, triglycerides, ALI, AST, WBC, GGT. May produce false-positive pregnancy test result.",
