        "text": "13 YRS AND OLDER: Initially, 25 mg twice daily on day 1, 50 mg twice daily on day 2, then increase by 100 mg/day to target dose of 400 mg twice daily on day 5. May further increase to 800 mg/ day in increments of 100 mg or less daily. Range: 400-800 mg/day. Maximum: 800 mg. Total dose in 3 divided doses. (Extended-Release): Initially, 50 mg once daily on day 1, 100 mg on day 2, until 400 mg once daily is reached on day 5. Range: 400-800 mg/ day. Maximum: 800 mg/day.",
